            <li>Accuracy of all information</li>
            <li>Compatibility with all devices/browsers</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>9.2 Limitation of Liability</h3>
          <p>
            To the maximum extent permitted by law, WorldBridger One and its contributors
            shall not be liable for:
          </p>
